page.title: 20CHURCH,WOODLAND,CREDITS
page.content:
{ Great Warford Baptist Chapel The chapel was founded at Norbury Houses in 1642. A service is held every Sunday, to which about 25 people come from a wide area. { {Woodland Sandle Heath is surrounded by ammunition dumps from the last war. These are now let out to farmers for storage. Soss Moss Wood is deciduous. The trees are mainly silver birch, oak and pine. There is also sycamore,rhododendron and hawthorn.
